data.description: This cozy home has been meticulously cared for. Home sits on a cul-de-sac at back of neighborhood. It is a must see for any homebuyers or investors to use as a rental property. It has an eat-in kitchen, large pantry and laundry room. Primary has a combination tub/shower and walk-in closet. Berber carpet in all bedrooms. Spacious backyard for entertaining. Large shed in the back. Great, established neighborhood with lots of amenities including: pool, clubhouse, volleyball court, tennis court, jogging trails and playground. Roof was redone in 2021, water heater in 2021 and ALL the siding was replaced and painted in 2022. This is a must show at this price point. Just a few minutes from 1604.
